        "value": "RODECaster Pro II",
        "annotation": "fef52656-5044-4445-868f-adb4db19b374"
      },
      {
        "id": "fb9cface-b860-4f05-b3d3-8446f4b69bc8",
        "purpose": "describing",
        "value": "This audio interface is state-of-the art, offering a ton of features and customizations, including sound effects and the ability to record via Zoom or Bluetooth. However, it still fits our \"one-button start\" goal, as you really can turn it on, press record, and get started. The machine can record to a USB drive or a straight into an audio editor on a laptop.",
        "annotation": "fef52656-5044-4445-868f-adb4db19b374"
